caption.p: Immunohistochemical analysis of oral squamous cell carcinoma specimens and adjacent normal tissues for CCR8 and P2RY14 protein. (A) CCR8 was highly expressed in tumor specimens of HNSCC patients compared to normal tissues. P2RY14 was highly expressed in normal tissues compared to tumor specimens. (B) The quantification of IHC results (FDR adjusted P-value < 0.05).
